{"tid":303562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警方威脅開始集會將展開拘捕行動】","createTime":"2017-06-30T09:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T11:12:47.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f704baf0532c91b899b21f630032ccd8f1e73bc1","tid":303562,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"【1723　警方威脅開始集會將展開拘捕行動】<br />\n<br />\n由於尖沙咀鐘樓被警方及康文署嚴密封鎖，敝黨早前轉往鄰近尖東市政局百周年紀念公園架設講台，惟遭警方阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n警民關係科警員警告召集人陳浩天，如敝黨成員開始佈置場地，將會立即拘捕。現時大量警察正於該處抄身份證及搜身，請支持者避免在該處聚集。<br />\n<br />\n請保持留意敝黨Facebook專頁或telegram channel之最新消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qdbjvo8a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqdbjvo8a&h=44290521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=673153892883568&amp;id=468882569977369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D673153892883568%26id%3D468882569977369&d=pfJr2N3EbyKllZWmyWlzgDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=355e0370\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=673153892883568&amp;id=468882569977369</a>"},{"pid":"2015e87dc98e4c21218293c6b2c077ef81e70b2f","tid":303562,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f270db0702469a21fc14cc5698bc2e2782795189","tid":303562,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcb6c3271cf0f565de4fc256d756a59c4a2c599","tid":303562,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"自己去睇海景行街都唔得？咁你班狗掃晒旺角班老坑先講嘢"},{"pid":"736c70226e7053e1dfc2d8eb15d5fc2518777827","tid":303562,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"<